          "401": {
            "description": "Unauthorized"
          },
          "403": {
            "description": "Forbidden"
          },
          "500": {
            "description": "Internal server error"
          }
        },
        "summary": "Phase 3 — per-sales-person-Tages-Sicht (PLAN-01). Analog zu\n[`get_shiftplan_week_for_sales_person`], aber liefert nur den einen\n`day_of_week` als Aggregat über alle Shiftplans.",
